{"title":"球迷购票","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3240","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>盛况空前的足球赛即将举行。球赛门票售票处排起了球迷购票长龙。按售票处规定，每位购票者限购一张门票，且每张票售价为50元。在排成长龙的球迷中有m个人手持面值50元的钱币，另有n个人手持面值100元的钱币。假设售票处在开始售票时没有零钱。试问这m+n个球迷有多少种排队方式可使售票处不致出现找不出钱的尴尬局面。</p>\n<p>例如当m=3，n=2时，用A表示手持面值50元钱币的球迷，用B表示手持面值100元钱币的球迷，则最多可得到以下5组不同排队方式，使售票处不致出现找不出钱的尴尬局面。</p>\n<p>售票处 A A A B B</p>\n<p>售票处 A A B A B</p>\n<p>售票处 A B A A B</p>\n<p>售票处 A A B B A</p>\n<p>售票处 A B A B A</p>\n<p>对于给定的m和n的值( 0 &lt; m，n &lt;30)，编程计算出m+n个球迷有多少种排队方式可使售票处不致出现找不出钱的尴尬局面。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入m和n的值。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出计算出的排队方式数。（注意：结果请用long long）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"266\">\n<p>ticket.in</p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"274\">\n<p>ticket.out</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"266\">\n<p>3 2</p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"274\">\n<p>5</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"266\">\n<p>ticket.in</p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"274\">\n<p>ticket.out</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"266\">\n<p>3 2</p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"274\">\n<p>5</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>无</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}